caption.text:
Hi, my name is Marco Orlando and I'm supporting XSProject!

XSProject is a non-profit organization that works to improve the lives of families living in Jakarta's trash picker communities by transforming the trash they picked into high-quality products with Batik theme as Indonesia's tradition.

XSProject has redirected and used more than 50 tons of trash that were destined for the garbage dump, produced and sold over 100,000 products, engaged 600+ people in the collection of trash and the production of our goods and provided a K-12 education for more than 100 trash picker children.

Go follow @xspcatalog to show your concern about their lives. Improving the life quality, caring the environment sustainability!

Find out more on http://www.xsproject-id.org/

#XSPcatalog #XSProject #betterJKT #awmp16 #accenture #gogreen
